%h1 Get Aeolus

.section-grouping
  Aeolus has (bleeding edge)
  %b Testing
  packages available, for Fedora 15, Fedora 16, and RHEL/CentOS 6.2. 64-bit only.

  %p
    %h2 Choose your installation instructions:

  %ul
    %li
      %b Install the
